79b/10-years-of-being-picked-on-by-iphone-users</a><br />\n正常人點會用乜撚what app WeChat 嗰啲垃圾..嗰啲人就梗係會開口埋口悶<br />\n下部電話可能要識飛先叫做有新意同創新"},{"pid":"0eca3cbffe648a53dabcfc46200e375c80ef00f9","tid":1962511,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"752714bb021b347ca8ad8dcf1744b61ea125dee4","tid":1962511,"uid":175032,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2ec327fe4dff873001244272640a3acb09d03bb9","tid":1962511,"uid":21488,"like":23,"dislike":36,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"7325262d4291e7732fc3e1ff7f6dcf6004792f49","tid":1962511,"uid":124,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T13:45:08.000Z","msg":"買s10 試下 唔洗蝕咁多"},"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T13:47:30.000Z","msg":"錢 我從來唔care 我用 就要用最頂尖"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T10:25:07.000Z","msg":"唔care錢用頂尖就咪撚買50k錶仔喇<br />\n綠水鬼都買唔撚到呀點出黎威呀大哥<br />\n<br />\n50K 筆直FG想買錶 想帶出黎威，有咩推薦？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1824690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1824690</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:39:14.000Z","msg":"有冇業餘工藝師既手作原post?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43733260d23ba28fe07c4685adbc63ad8c570198","tid":1962511,"uid":194281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"韓國機,S3死底板<br />\nG3 先天設計自動黑MON<br />\n2部都過唔到2年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb74bfed2fd944d30107d347c502cfdfbfd1196d","tid":1962511,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0eca3cbffe648a53dabcfc46200e375c80ef00f9","tid":1962511,"uid":55458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"752714bb021b347ca8ad8dcf1744b61ea125dee4","tid":1962511,"uid":175032,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2ec327fe4dff873001244272640a3acb09d03bb9","tid":1962511,"uid":21488,"like":23,"dislike"